# Background Functions Deploy Trigger

The deploy workflow (.github/workflows/deploy-background-functions.yml) only
runs on pushes to `main` that change a file under
`api/src/functions/background/**`. Touch this file and push to force a redeploy
of all background Lambda functions without changing any function source.

The deploy job iterates over directories only, so this top-level file is
ignored when packaging — it serves purely as a trigger.

